Project: fs/lustre-release&lt;br/&gt;
Branch: master&lt;br/&gt;
Current Patch Set: &lt;br/&gt;
Commit: db0b09018e77114667a1b0fbd6c04194f56cb492&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="308440" author="ashehata" created="Mon, 26 Jul 2021 16:51:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We should also add a patch to reset the individual network and peer statistics. It would be good to roll that into the net/peer commands. Something like:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
lnetctl peer reset-stats 
lnetctl peer reset-stats --nid &amp;lt;&amp;gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;this will allow us to reset all the net/peers or only the specified nid.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="306280" author="gerrit" created="Tue, 6 Jul 2021 12:27:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Cyril Bordage (cbordage@whamcloud.com) uploaded a new patch: &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/44150&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/44150&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
